    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in unparalleled showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every facet, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, exemplifies meticulous ownership and rigorous care. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the discerning driver. Experience a standard of excellence that transcends the typical pre-owned market.",
