      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for a new home. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
