    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered era. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled and bulletproofed with machined hubs. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a reinforced rear subframe to prevent the common fatigue points associated with this platform. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every suspension component remains factory-spec, featuring fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers that maintain the original kinematics. Compression and leak-down tests show nominal factory values across all cylinders, confirming the integrity of the rotating assembly. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the technical purist.",
